reviews.review_text: All it takes is one screaming maniac to ruin it !!! I was at this show and the one previous there and the Minn.Mn.show that followed. The first night at the Mecca Rocked. I had 2nd row at the Mecca sitting in front of Phil both nights with a recently broken shoulder. My internal Organs vibrated being so close,I Was glad he didn't drop his Sonic bass bomb note for fear my Liver might Explode! Ha!!! It was incredible!!! Thanks Phil We Love you!!! I was very,very glad to down load the shows I could. But sadly discovered The screaming maniac on this recording.All destroying the respectful hard work of the tapers who labored so hard for us to be able to enjoy there worthy efforts of kindness!!! Thank you for this show!!! I give the Band a 4 and the tapers efforts a 5 for being there and knock it down for the screaming maniac who on his own destroyed it.Sorry but I give it a 3, I am just being plain honest,we can only blame him now years and years later!!!  What a shame!!!
nice surprisingly amazing sound. never would have thought to use omnis indoors like this.  great pull!
